{"tid":2114354,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要好好感謝身邊嘅人仍然生存緊，因為選擇活下去真係唔容易。","createTime":"2020-07-18T18:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T03:24:14.000Z","uid":218219,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c737b5dc01c52477fd2865b3034da6812de535","tid":2114354,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T18:15:10.000Z","msg":"我有諗過用「珍惜」呢個詞，但最後都係覺得「感謝」比較貼近我諗法。<br />\n由鍾鉉到雪莉到荷拉到三浦春馬，仲有香港上年好多自殺死嘅手足<br />\n其實每個人呢刻仲係你身邊，唔係必然嘅事<br />\n的確佢冇病冇痛冇意外，但佢其實大可以選擇放棄生存<br />\n每個人都有自己嘅難處，其他人就算設身處地去諗都未必能夠體會有幾辛苦<br />\n人前可能扮到好樂觀，好似冇事咁<br />\n但佢內心流曬血都未必想畀人知道<br />\n所以比起老土嘅一句「珍惜眼前人」，亦要有感謝嘅心：<br />\n感謝佢明明過得咁辛苦，呢刻仍然選擇咗活下來陪伴自己<br />\n<br />\n當你諗到自己都唔想身邊人死嘅時候<br />\n希望你明白，你身邊嘅人都係咁樣諗緊你<br />\n你其實並唔係咁孤單。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你出現在我的世界上。"},{"pid":"479bc0f3b7ebe1681d8ec59ca7033ed4af31ed18","tid":2114354,"uid":262406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T18:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395294273189e1862ce31243557b41d21ff74b82","tid":2114354,"uid":218219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"479bc0f3b7ebe1681d8ec59ca7033ed4af31ed18","tid":2114354,"uid":262406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T18:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T18:17:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XjLQjlmxRe4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXjLQjlmxRe4&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=937bdfcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XjLQjlmxRe4</a><br />\n依家睇翻《戀空》主題曲歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309bcfe3a6e872bd3aaed4395238a309308